    hr
    .container-fluid
      .container.project-section.process
        .row.section-title
                .col-md-12.text-center
                    h3 Process
            .row.section-content
                .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Research Current Product
                                p The focus of the project is to improve usability. Therefore, I started the process with 
                                    b usability testing
                                    |  of the old version. I discoverd that:
                                ul
                                    li Users do not know where to seek help
                                    li Users often get confused by pop-overs
                                    li Experienced users often get frustrated when they need to complete a simple task with multiple steps

                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-1.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Contextual Inquiry & User Stories
                                p Based on the usability test, I proposed various 
                                    b user stories 
                                    | and also conducted 
                                    b Contextual Inquiry 
                                    | .
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-2.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Wireframing
                                p A wireframe model was then made for another round of 
                                    b user testing. 
                                    | Users are asked to go through a set of tasks and 
                                    b Thinking Aloud 
                                    | when doing them. 
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-3.svg")
                    
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 High Fidelity Design
                                p A high fidelity design was created using 
                                    b Illustrator 
                                    | based on the discoveries and feedbacks gathered from the 
                                    b user testing
                                    | .
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-4.svg")
                        
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.process-content-wrapper
                            .process-content-container
                                h4 Final Deliverable
                                p Finally, I turned the design into code and handed it over to back-end engineer for integration
                        .col-md-6
                            img(src="/images/pandafan-process-5.svg")
                        
                    
                        

                    
