        .container.project-section.conclusion
            .row.section-title
                    .col-md-12.text-center
                        h3 Conclusion
                .row.section-content
                    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                        p This project allowed me to practice the design principles I learned in my Interaction Design class. The design pipeline I practiced made my design more 
                            b user-centric
                            |  – every design decision is derived from user requirement. It is a good learning experience for me as I had the chance to practice what I learned beyond school projects.


